great book for engineering students this book is great for students who are thinking of persuing a course in engineering . ferguson adresses what makes a great engineer , and also states that many schools do not stress the courses they should . using this book , students gain insight as to what they should expect from being an engineer , and what is imporant in the profession . i definately recommend this book to those who are about to be college freshman engineers or are thinking of changing over from liberal arts & amp ; sciences to engineering